data.description: Under Construction. Beautiful New 3-bedroom 2 bath home under construction in Plant City. This home features an open floor plan with nearly 1,600 square feet; luxurious 10 feet ceilings; a 2-car garage and private a covered lanai. Enjoy movie theater, shopping, restaurants all just a short walk away.  Easily commute to nearby Brandon, Tampa, and Lakeland with close proximity to US Hwy 60 or I-4. With Construction nearly complete by local builder Block Services LLC there is time to choose your own paint; fixtures flooring. Hurry this one won't last long.
